    "display_name": "Fix the Layout",
    "long_instructions": "#Fix the Layout\r\n\r\nWith the help of AI, fix the spacing, alignment, and layout problems so the page feels clean and consistent.\r\n   - Consider focusing on issues such as:\r\n      - Even spacing between cards\r\n      - Centering and alignment of sections\r\n      - Consistent image sizing and card heights\r\n      - Footer alignment and spacing",
    "bubble_choice_description": "Fix layout issues such as spacing and alignment.",
    "thumbnail_url": "https://images.code.org/1fec9cb6841e171b1e2ac2a3085e48de-layout.png",
    "start_sources": {
      "folders": {
      },
      "files": {
        "1": {
          "id": "1",
          "name": "index.html",
          "language": "html",
          "contents": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>NoiseLab — Music Club Showcase</title>\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"styles.css\" />\n</head>\n<body>\n  <a class=\"skip-link\" href=\"#main\">Skip to content</a>\n\n  <header class=\"site-header\">\n    <div class=\"container header-inner\">\n      <a class=\"brand\" href=\"#home\">\n        <span class=\"logo\" aria-hidden=\"true\">♬</span>\n        <span class=\"brand-name\">NoiseLab</span>\n      </a>\n\n      <nav class=\"primary-nav\" aria-label=\"Primary\">\n        <ul class=\"nav\">\n          <li><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"#shows\">Shows</a></li>\n          <li><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"#playlists\">Playlists</a></li>\n          <li><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"#join\">Join</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </nav>\n    </div>\n  </header>\n\n  <main id=\"main\">\n    <!-- HERO (misaligned on purpose) -->\n    <section class=\"hero\" id=\"home\">\n      <div class=\"hero-inner\">\n        <h1>Music Club Showcase</h1>\n        <p class=\"lede\">\n          Discover student bands, open mics, and curated playlists.\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"hero-actions\">\n          <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"#shows\">See Upcoming Shows</a>\n          <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"#playlists\">Browse Playlists</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <img class=\"hero-art\" src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/poster/980/500\" alt=\"Poster collage\" />\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- SHOW GRID (gaps/widths broken on purpose) -->\n    <section class=\"shows\" id=\"shows\" aria-label=\"Upcoming shows\">\n      <div class=\"section-header\">\n        <h2>Upcoming Shows</h2>\n        <p class=\"sub\">Lineups from the next few weeks</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"show-grid\">\n        <article class=\"show-card\">\n          <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/a/420/290\" alt=\"Band A poster\" />\n          <h3>Friday Night — Gym Stage</h3>\n          <p>Three bands. Doors at 6. Bring your student ID.</p>\n        </article>\n\n        <article class=\"show-card tall\">\n          <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/b/520/220\" alt=\"Band B poster\" />\n          <h3>Open Mic — Commons</h3>\n          <p>Acoustic sets and poetry. Sign up early!</p>\n        </article>\n\n        <article class=\"show-card\">\n          <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/c/360/400\" alt=\"Band C poster\" />\n          <h3>Battle of the Bands</h3>\n          <p>Vote for your favorite set. Prizes + food trucks.</p>\n        </article>\n\n        <article class=\"show-card\">\n          <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/d/480/260\" alt=\"Band D poster\" />\n          <h3>Jazz Night — Auditorium</h3>\n          <p>Small ensembles and featured soloists.</p>\n        </article>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- PLAYLISTS (alignment & spacing issues) -->\n    <section class=\"playlists\" id=\"playlists\" aria-label=\"Club playlists\">\n      <div class=\"section-header off-center\">\n        <h2>Playlists</h2>\n        <p class=\"sub\">Curated by student DJs</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"playlist-row\">\n        <article class=\"playlist\">\n          <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/pl1/320/320\" alt=\"Playlist cover\" />\n          <div class=\"pl-meta\">\n            <h3>Focus Beats</h3>\n            <p>Lo-fi, ambient, and calm synths</p>\n          </div>\n        </article>\n\n        <article class=\"playlist\">\n          <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/pl2/280/320\" alt=\"Playlist cover\" />\n          <div class=\"pl-meta\">\n            <h3>Hype Mix</h3>\n            <p>High-energy tracks for practice</p>\n          </div>\n        </article>\n\n        <article class=\"playlist\">\n          <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/pl3/360/260\" alt=\"Playlist cover\" />\n          <div class=\"pl-meta\">\n            <h3>Indie Finds</h3>\n            <p>New sounds from small artists</p>\n          </div>\n        </article>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- JOIN (padding/width oddities) -->\n    <section class=\"join\" id=\"join\" aria-label=\"Join the club\">\n      <h2>Join the Club</h2>\n      <p>We meet Tuesdays after school in Room 214.</p>\n      <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"#apply\">Apply Now</a>\n    </section>\n  </main>\n\n  <footer class=\"site-footer\">\n    <div class=\"footer-inner\">\n      <p>© 2025 NoiseLab Music Club</p>\n      <nav aria-label=\"Footer\">\n        <ul class=\"nav footer-nav\">\n          <li><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"#code\">Code of Conduct</a></li>\n          <li><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </nav>\n    </div>\n  </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n",
          "active": false,
          "folderId": "0"
        },
        "2": {
          "id": "2",
          "name": "styles.css",
          "language": "css",
          "contents": "/* =========================\n   Students should fix spacing, alignment, wrapping, and sizing.\n   ========================= */\n\n/* ---- Tokens ---- */\n:root{\n  --accent: #e11d48;\n  --surface: #ffffff;\n  --bg: #f6f7fb;\n  --text: #1f2937;\n  --muted: #6b7280;\n  --border: #e5e7eb;\n\n  --radius: 12px;\n  --radius-sm: 8px;\n\n  --space-1: 4px;\n  --space-2: 8px;\n  --space-3: 12px;\n  --space-4: 16px;\n  --space-6: 24px;\n  --space-8: 32px;\n  --space-10: 40px;\n\n  --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.06);\n  --shadow-md: 0 10px 22px rgba(0,0,0,.12);\n}\n\n/* ---- Base ---- */\n*{ box-sizing: border-box; }\nhtml, body{ margin:0; padding:0; }\nbody{\n  font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial;\n  color: var(--text);\n  background: var(--bg);\n  line-height: 1.5;\n}\nimg{ max-width: 100%; display: block; }\nh1,h2,h3{ line-height: 1.2; margin: 0 0 var(--space-3) 0; }\np{ margin: 0 0 var(--space-3) 0; }\n\n/* Skip link */\n.skip-link{ position:absolute; left:-9999px; top:auto; }\n.skip-link:focus{ left:16px; top:16px; background:#000; color:#fff; padding:8px 12px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); }\n\n/* =========================\n   Containers & Header (off-center + cramped)\n   ========================= */\n\n/* POLISH TARGET: container uses fixed width + side margin, not centered */\n.container{\n  width: 980px;\n  margin-left: 18px;     /* pushes whole layout to the right */\n  margin-right: 0;\n  padding: 0 10px;       /* arbitrary */\n}\n\n.site-header{\n  background: var(--surface);\n  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n}\n.header-inner{\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  padding: 8px 0;        /* cramped vertically */\n}\n.brand{\n  display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap: var(--space-2);\n  text-decoration:none; color: var(--text); font-weight: 800;\n}\n.logo{ color: var(--accent); font-size: 1.1rem; }\n\n.nav{ display:flex; gap: 28px; list-style:none; margin:0 6px 0 0; padding:0; } /* big, uneven gap */\n.nav-link{ text-decoration:none; color: var(--text); padding: 4px 6px; }\n\n/* =========================\n   HERO (overlap + crowding)\n   ========================= */\n.hero{\n  background: var(--surface);\n  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n  padding: 10px 0 14px;           /* thin and uneven */\n  position: relative;\n}\n.hero .container{ width: 930px; } /* different from other containers → drift */\n.hero-inner{\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.1fr;\n  column-gap: 10px;               /* too tight */\n  align-items: start;             /* not vertically centered */\n  transform: translateX(-6px);    /* shoves grid left */\n}\n.lede{ color: var(--muted); }\n.hero-actions{ display:flex; gap: 10px; margin-top: 12px; }\n\n/* Oversized hero image that intrudes on text column */\n.hero-art{\n  position: relative;\n  width: 122%;                    /* clearly too wide */\n  left: -22px;                    /* creeps into left margin */\n  margin-top: 6px;\n  border-radius: var(--radius);\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);\n}\n\n/* =========================\n   SHOWS (ragged grid)\n   ========================= */\n.shows{ padding: 12px 0; }        /* inconsistent section spacing */\n.section-header{\n  margin: 0 10px 8px 20px;        /* random offsets vs container */\n}\n.section-header .sub{ color: var(--muted); }\n\n/* POLISH TARGET: flex + manual widths cause jagged wrapping + uneven gaps */\n.show-grid{\n  display: flex;\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\n  gap: 14px 8px;                  /* row/col gaps mismatched */\n  padding: 0 8px;\n}\n\n/* One card too wide; others too narrow */\n.show-card{\n  background: var(--surface);\n  border: 1px solid var(--border);\n  border-radius: var(--radius);\n  padding: 12px;\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  width: 31%;                     /* odd three-up width (doesn't divide gaps well) */\n}\n.show-card:first-child{ width: 62%; }  /* jarring imbalance on first row */\n.show-card:nth-child(3){ width: 46%; } /* random width makes row wrap weirdly */\n\n.show-card img{\n  width: 100%;\n  height: 215px;                  /* fixed height with mixed sources */\n  object-fit: cover;\n  border-radius: var(--radius);\n  margin-bottom: 10px;\n}\n/* Height hack that breaks alignment */\n.show-card.tall p{ margin-bottom: 36px; }\n\n/* =========================\n   PLAYLISTS (crooked sizes + spacing)\n   ========================= */\n.playlists{\n  background: var(--surface);\n  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);\n  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n  padding: 10px 0;                /* tight */\n}\n.off-center{ margin-left: 26px; } /* clearly off from container center */\n\n.playlist-row{\n  display: flex;                  /* flex with uneven fixed widths → crooked line */\n  gap: 12px;\n  padding: 0 10px;\n}\n.playlist{\n  width: 26%;                     /* not adding up to full row with gaps */\n  display: flex;\n  gap: 10px;\n  align-items: stretch;           /* makes heights feel odd */\n  border: 1px solid var(--border);\n  border-radius: var(--radius);\n  padding: 10px;\n}\n.playlist:nth-child(2){ width: 38%; }     /* middle card much wider */\n.playlist img{\n  width: 104px; height: 130px;    /* inconsistent aspect ratio */\n  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);\n  object-fit: cover;\n}\n.pl-meta p{ color: var(--muted); }\n\n/* =========================\n   JOIN (width + centering off)\n   ========================= */\n.join{\n  width: 87%;                     /* differs from container */\n  margin-left: 5%;                /* extra offset */\n  padding: 10px 0 8px;            /* random values */\n  text-align: center;\n}\n\n/* =========================\n   FOOTER (crammed & hugging edge)\n   ========================= */\n.site-footer{\n  background: var(--surface);\n  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);\n  margin-top: 12px;\n}\n.footer-inner{\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: center;\n  padding: 6px 4px;               /* very tight; text close to edges */\n}\n.footer-nav .nav-link{ color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; }\n\n/* =========================\n   Buttons (kept simple; not main target here)\n   ========================= */\n.btn{\n  display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;\n  padding: 10px 14px;\n  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);\n  border: 1px solid var(--border);\n  background: var(--surface);\n  color: var(--text);\n  text-decoration: none;\n}\n.btn-primary{ background: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); color: #fff; }\n.btn-secondary{ color: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); }\n",
          "folderId": "0",
          "active": true
        }
      },
      "openFiles": [
        "1",
        "2"
      ]
    },
